<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- JS, Popper.js, and jQuery -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Rapport d'activité</h1>
    <hr>
    <br>
    <h3 id="mois">Mois :
        <%=mois%>
            <%= year %>
    </h3>


    <h4>Mission</h4>
    <div>
        <p>Nom prestataire :
            <%=prestataire%>
        </p>
        <p>Nom du client :
            <%=client%>
        </p>
        <p>Intitulé de la mission :
            <%= mission %>
        </p>
    </div>

    <h4>Durée de la prestation : 1 unité de facturation = 1 journée travaillé</h4>

    <div class="calendar">
        <% for(var i=0; i <daysInMonth.length;  i++ ) { %>
            <div class="cell">
                <div class="cell-header">
                    <%=i + 1 %>
                </div>

                <div class="cell-content">
                    <% if(daysInMonth[i].is_bd) {%>
                        1
                        <% } else { %>
                            0
                            <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

    </div>

    <div>Total :
        <%= business_days.length %>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div>Validation :</div>
    <div id="sides">
        <div id="left">
            <div class="leftbox">Intervenant <br> (date, nom, prénom, signature obligatoire)</div>
        </div>

        <div id="right">
            <div class="rightbox">Client <br> (date, nom, prénom, signature obligatoire) </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <div>
        <b>Je soussigné, certifie l'exactitude des prestations reportées ci-dessus ainsi que sa bonne exécution pour la facturation conforme aux accords commerciaux signés</b>
    </div>
    <br>
</body>

</html>

<style>
    body {
        padding: 3.5cm;
    }
    
    h1 {
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    #mois {
        text-align: right;
        border: 2.5px;
        border-style: solid;
        border-color: black;
        margin-left: 500px;
        padding: 5px 20px 2px 20px;
        display: inline;
    }
    
    .cell {
        width: 100px;
        height: 50px;
        float: left;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 3px 2px 3px 2px;
        border: 2px solid black;
    }
    
    .cell-header {
        background-color: darksalmon;
    }
    
    .cell-content {
        background-color: cornflowerblue;
    }
    
    .calendar {
        overflow: auto;
        margin: 0px 50px 0 50px;
    }
    
    #sides {
        margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;
    }
    
    #left {
        float: left;
        width: 50%;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    #right {
        width: 50%;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .rightbox {
        border: 2px solid black;
        margin: 0px 0px 0px 170px;
        padding: 2px 2px 100px 2px;
    }
    
    .leftbox {
        border: 2px solid black;
        margin: 0px 170px 0px 0px;
        padding: 2px 2px 100px 2px;
    }
    
    html {
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    }
</style>